<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <meta name="description" content="Account Guardian pricing — $79/month flat rate. 14-day free trial, cancel anytime. No credit card required to start.">
  <title>Pricing — Account Guardian by Astramedia</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/theme.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0A0A0F;
      --bg-surface: #111118;
      --bg-card: #16161F;
      --fg: #E8E8F0;
      --fg-muted: #6B6B80;
      --cyan: #00E5FF;
      --cyan-dim: rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.12);
      --green: #B4FF00;
      --green-dim: rgba(180, 255, 0, 0.12);
      --red: #FF3B5C;
      --border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
      --font-head: 'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
      --font-mono: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body { background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg); font-family: var(--font-head); -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased; overflow-x: hidden; }
    a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }

    /* NAV */
    .nav {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      padding: 20px 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(10,10,15,0.95);
      backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
      z-index: 100;
    }
    .nav-brand { font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .nav-brand span { font-size: 0.65em; opacity: 0.65; vertical-align: super; }
    .nav-links { display: flex; gap: 28px; align-items: center; }
    .nav-links a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg-muted); transition: color 0.15s; }
    .nav-links a:hover { color: var(--fg); }
    .nav-links a.active { color: var(--fg); }
    .nav-cta { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 16px; font-size: 14px; }
    .nav-email { font-family: var(--font-mono); color: var(--fg-muted); font-size: 13px; }
    .btn-nav { display: inline-block; border: 1px solid var(--cyan); color: var(--cyan); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 13px; font-weight: 600; padding: 8px 16px; border-radius: 4px; transition: all 0.2s; }
    .btn-nav:hover { background: var(--cyan-dim); }

    /* PAGE */
    .page-wrap { padding: 80px 48px 120px; max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; }
    .page-eyebrow { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 500; letter-spacing: 0.15em; color: var(--cyan); background: var(--cyan-dim); padding: 6px 12px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 24px; display: inline-block; }
    .page-title { font-size: clamp(32px, 4vw, 52px); font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.02em; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .page-sub { font-size: 18px; color: var(--fg-muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 580px; margin-bottom: 64px; }

    /* PLAN CARD */
    .plan-card {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 20px;
      padding: 48px 56px;
      max-width: 540px;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }
    .plan-card::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: -40px; right: -40px;
      width: 160px; height: 160px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--cyan-dim);
      pointer-events: none;
    }
    .plan-badge { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 11px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.12em; color: var(--cyan); background: var(--cyan-dim); padding: 5px 12px; border-radius: 2px; margin-bottom: 28px; display: inline-block; }
    .plan-name { font-size: 24px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    .plan-price { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 6px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .plan-price .amt { font-size: 64px; font-weight: 700; font-family: var(--font-mono); letter-spacing: -0.03em; line-height: 1; }
    .plan-price .per { font-size: 18px; color: var(--fg-muted); }
    .plan-desc { font-size: 15px; color: var(--fg-muted); margin-bottom: 36px; }

    /* FEATURES LIST */
    .feature-list { list-style: none; margin-bottom: 40px; }
    .feature-list li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 12px; font-size: 15px; padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    .feature-list li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .check { color: var(--green); font-size: 16px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 1px; }

    /* CTA */
    .plan-cta { }
    .plan-cta .btn-trial {
      display: block;
      background: var(--cyan);
      color: #0A0A0F;
      font-family: var(--font-head);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 17px;
      padding: 18px 36px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      transition: opacity 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .plan-cta .btn-trial:hover { opacity: 0.9; box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(0, 229, 255, 0.4); }
    .plan-cta .btn-logged-in {
      display: block;
      background: var(--green-dim);
      color: var(--green);
      font-family: var(--font-head);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 17px;
      padding: 18px 36px;
      border-radius: 4px;
      text-align: center;
      border: 1px solid rgba(180,255,0,0.2);
      transition: opacity 0.2s;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .plan-cta .btn-logged-in:hover { opacity: 0.85; }
    .plan-note { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-muted); text-align: center; font-family: var(--font-mono); }

    /* GUARANTEES */
    .guarantees { display: flex; gap: 32px; margin-top: 48px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
    .guarantee { flex: 1; min-width: 200px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 14px; padding: 20px; background: var(--bg-surface); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; }
    .guarantee-icon { font-size: 24px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .guarantee strong { display: block; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; }
    .guarantee span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg-muted); line-height: 1.5; }

    /* LOGGED-IN STATE */
    .logged-in-banner {
      background: var(--bg-card);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 24px 32px;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 20px;
    }
    .logged-in-banner .li-text { font-size: 15px; color: var(--fg-muted); }
    .logged-in-banner .li-text strong { color: var(--fg); }

    /* FAQ */
    .faq-section { margin-top: 72px; }
    .faq-title { font-size: 28px; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 32px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .faq-item { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding: 20px 0; }
    .faq-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .faq-q { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px; cursor: pointer; }
    .faq-a { font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg-muted); line-height: 1.7; display: none; }
    .faq-item.open .faq-a { display: block; }
    .faq-item.open .faq-q { color: var(--cyan); }

    /* BACK LINK */
    .back-link { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--fg-muted); margin-bottom: 48px; transition: color 0.15s; }
    .back-link:hover { color: var(--fg); }
    .back-link:hover svg path { stroke: var(--fg); }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .page-wrap { padding: 40px 24px 80px; }
      .plan-card { padding: 32px 28px; }
      .plan-price .amt { font-size: 48px; }
      .nav { padding: 16px 24px; }
      .nav-links { display: none; }
      .guarantees { flex-direction: column; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-brand">Account Guardian <span>by Astramedia</span></div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="/#features">Features</a>
    <a href="/pricing" class="active">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/audit">Free Audit</a>
  </div>
  <div class="nav-cta">
    <% if (userEmail) { %>
      <span class="nav-email"><%= userEmail %></span>
      <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-nav">Dashboard</a>
      <a href="#" id="logout-link" class="btn-nav" style="cursor:pointer; background:none; border:none; color:var(--cyan);">Sign Out</a>
    <% } else { %>
      <a href="/auth/login" class="btn-nav" style="margin-right: 8px;">Sign In</a>
      <a href="/auth/signup" class="btn-nav">Get Started</a>
    <% } %>
  </div>
</nav>

<div class="page-wrap">

  <!-- BACK -->
  <a href="/" class="back-link">
    <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none"><path d="M19 12H5M12 5l-7 7 7 7" stroke="var(--fg-muted)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
    Back to home
  </a>

  <!-- HEADER -->
  <div class="page-eyebrow">PRICING</div>
  <h1 class="page-title">Simple. One plan. No surprises.</h1>
  <p class="page-sub">Everything you need to protect your Stripe account — daily monitoring, threshold alerts, and actionable remediation guides — in one flat rate.</p>

  <!-- LOGGED-IN BANNER -->
  <% if (userEmail) { %>
  <div class="logged-in-banner">
    <div class="li-text">Signed in as <strong><%= userEmail %></strong></div>
    <a href="/dashboard" class="btn-nav" style="background: var(--cyan-dim);">Go to Dashboard →</a>
  </div>
  <% } %>

  <!-- PLAN CARD -->
  <div class="plan-card">
    <div class="plan-badge">MOST POPULAR</div>
    <div class="plan-name">Account Guardian</div>
    <div class="plan-price">
      <span class="amt">$79</span>
      <span class="per">/month</span>
    </div>
    <div class="plan-desc">Everything included. Cancel anytime.</div>

    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Daily monitoring of all 5 risk signals</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Threshold alerts with real numbers</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Actionable remediation guides</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Weekly account health digest</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Alert history dashboard</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Stripe read-only connection</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Email alert delivery</li>
      <li><span class="check">✓</span> Priority support</li>
    </ul>

    <div class="plan-cta">
      <% if (userEmail) { %>
        <a href="/dashboard?billing=upgrade" class="btn-logged-in">Upgrade to Paid →</a>
        <p class="plan-note">Already on trial? Connect Stripe to activate.</p>
      <% } else { %>
        <a href="/buy" class="btn-trial">Start Your 14-Day Free Trial →</a>
        <p class="plan-note">No credit card required to start</p>
      <% } %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- GUARANTEES -->
  <div class="guarantees">
    <div class="guarantee">
      <div class="guarantee-icon">🛡</div>
      <div>
        <strong>14-day free trial</strong>
        <span>No credit card required. Start monitoring today.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="guarantee">
      <div class="guarantee-icon">💳</div>
      <div>
        <strong>Cancel anytime</strong>
        <span>No long-term contracts. Month-to-month.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="guarantee">
      <div class="guarantee-icon">🔒</div>
      <div>
        <strong>Read-only Stripe access</strong>
        <span>Your data stays yours. We never write to your account.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <div class="faq-section">
    <div class="faq-title">Common questions</div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">What's included in the 14-day free trial?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Full access to Account Guardian — daily monitoring, all 5 signal types, alert emails, and the dashboard. No credit card required. If you don't connect Stripe and subscribe within 14 days, monitoring stops.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">How does billing work?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">$79/month, billed monthly. No annual discount for now. Cancel at any time from your Settings page — you'll keep access until the end of the current billing period.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">What does "read-only Stripe connection" mean?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Account Guardian connects via Stripe Connect using read-only OAuth scope. We can only read your transaction data, dispute rates, and account metrics. We cannot initiate charges, refunds, or any write operations on your Stripe account.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">Which Stripe signals are monitored?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Five signals: dispute rate, auth/decline rate, revenue trend (week-over-week), transaction velocity, and low volume detection. Each is calibrated to your baseline after connecting.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">What happens if my thresholds are breached?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">You'll receive an email alert immediately, with a link to a specific remediation guide for that signal. You can acknowledge the alert in the dashboard or adjust thresholds if it's a false positive.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-item" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
      <div class="faq-q">Can I adjust my thresholds?</div>
      <div class="faq-a">Yes. After calibration, you can raise or lower any threshold in your dashboard. Changes take effect on the next daily scan.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div><!-- /.page-wrap -->

<script>
  function toggleFaq(el) {
    el.classList.toggle('open');
  }

  // Logout
  const logoutLink = document.getElementById('logout-link');
  if (logoutLink) {
    logoutLink.addEventListener('click', async (e) => {
      e.preventDefault();
      await fetch('/auth/logout', { method: 'POST' });
      window.location.href = '/';
    });
  }
</script>
